name: P2PSystemsProject
description: Handles call initiation, termination, call busy and waiting; Performs interaction with DHT (Distributed Hash Table) and KX (Key Exchange) modules. Generates pseudo-identities of callee, based on the DH (Diffe-Hellman) Key Exchange method and maintains session between caller and callee. Uses the RTP protocol to stream/exchange audio over the network reliably in real-time. Also performs self calling to mitigate profiling attacks.
